# Title: Sysmon Blocked Executable
# Author: Nasreddine Bencherchali (Nextron Systems)
# Date: 2022-08-16
# Level: high
# Description: Triggers on any Sysmon "FileBlockExecutable" event, which indicates a violation of the configured block policy
